Kenny Baker (English actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kenny_Baker_(English_actor) 0 Kenneth George Baker (24 August 1934 – 13 August 2016) was an English actor and musician. He is best remembered for portraying the character R2-D2 in the Star Wars science fiction movie franchise. Kenneth_George_Baker ( 24_August_1934 – 13_August_2016 ) was an_English_actor_and_musician .
